Package: softHybridImpute
Type: Package
Title: Soft Hybrid Imputation for Proteomics Missing Values
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Yixin", "Shi", 
           email = "yixin.shi@wolfson.ox.ac.uk", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides soft hybrid imputation for proteomics missing values
    by blending Random Forest and MinProb imputations with dynamic weighting
    based on protein missing rate and mean abundance. Includes visualization of weights.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: R (>= 4.1)
Imports:
    ggplot2,
    scales,
    grid,
    stats
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/YixinShiProteomics/softHybridImpute
BugReports: https://github.com/YixinShiProteomics/softHybridImpute/issues
